OL,3,C'Hearts broken' as funerals held for
OL,4,Cthree killed in Armagh crash
OL,6,FFuneral services for three of the four
OL,7,Fpeople killed in a single-car crash
OL,8,Fnear Armagh last weekend have taken
OL,9,Fplace on Good Friday.
OL,11,FMarina Crilly, 24, Emma Mallon, 22,
OL,12,FPhilip Mitchell, 27, and Keith
OL,13,FMorrison, 22, all from the Armagh
OL,14,Farea, were formally named by police on
OL,15,FWednesday as the victims of the road
OL,16,Fcrash last weekend.
OL,18,FThe collision, which involved a grey
OL,19,FVolkswagen Golf, happened on the
OL,20,FBallynahonemore Road at around 2.10am
OL,21,Fon Sunday.
