OL,6,FPolice said the driver and three
OL,7,Fpassengers were all declared dead at
OL,8,Fthe scene.
OL,10,FAt the funeral liturgy service for Ms
OL,11,FCrilly at St Patrick's Church,
OL,12,FBallymacnab, the priest said: "It is a
OL,13,Fvery sad day for all the families who
OL,14,Flost loved ones last Sunday morning."
OL,16,FHe paid tribute to the four young
OL,17,Fpeople killed in the crash: "Philip,
OL,18,FKeith, Emma and our own parishioner
OL,19,FMarina Crilly.
