OL,6,F"We all felt the shock and the
OL,7,Fdisbelief. We felt that such a tragedy
OL,8,Fcouldn't have happened and shouldn't
OL,9,Fhave happened.
OL,11,F"All the occupants were so young with
OL,12,Fa life ahead of them."
OL,14,FMs Crilly, a care home worker who was
OL,15,Fthe mother of a young boy, was
OL,16,Fremembered for her faith as well as
OL,17,Fher love of fashion and music.
