OL,6,FThe priest said: "Marina touched all
OL,7,Four lives and helped us keep alive the
OL,8,Fvalues and ideals she put before us;
OL,9,Fher kindness, her love, her
OL,10,Ffriendliness, her devotion to Our Lady
OL,11,Fand her devotion to her family."
OL,13,FAt the service for Mr Morrison, his
OL,14,Fcoffin was brought to the church on
OL,15,Fthe back of a lorry cab and several
OL,16,Ftractors also parked outside.
OL,18,FMr Morrison's step-mother Christine
OL,19,FWright delivered a tribute on behalf
OL,20,Fof the family.
