OL,6,FSpeaking during the service at
OL,7,FLislooney Presbyterian Church, Ms
OL,8,FWright said: "Such a kind, caring,
OL,9,Flovable, little rogue, the cheeky grin
OL,10,Fand the sparkle in his eyes. He would
OL,11,Fhave done anything to help anyone and
OL,12,Ftook great joy in helping out people `
OL,13,Fbut don't ask him during silage
OL,14,Fseason!"
OL,16,FShe added: "We are all so proud of
OL,17,Fthis young man and what he has
OL,18,Faccomplished in a short life. We want
OL,19,Fthis to be a celebration of a young
OL,20,Flife. We will miss him."
