OL,6,FMr Mitchell's funeral was also held on
OL,7,FFriday at First Armagh Presbyterian
OL,8,FChurch.
OL,10,FIn a statement, his family said:
OL,11,F"While our hearts are broken, our love
OL,12,Fand deepest sympathy goes out to the
OL,13,Ffamilies of Marina, Emma, and Keith,
OL,14,Fwho lost their lives so tragically
OL,15,Falong with Philip at the weekend. Even
OL,16,Fnow, it is just unthinkable what has
OL,17,Fhappened and we still can't really
OL,18,Ftake it in."
