OL,6,FThe statement adds: "Philip was more
OL,7,Fthan just a member of our family; he
OL,8,Fwas a bright light in the lives of all
OL,9,Fwho knew him.
OL,11,F"He had a zest for life that was
OL,12,Finfectious, a kind soul that touched
OL,13,Feveryone he met, and a smile that
OL,14,Fcould light up any room. He has left a
OL,15,Fhuge void in our lives that can never
OL,16,Fbe filled and we will never stop
OL,17,Fmissing him."
OL,19,FMs Mallon's funeral service will be
OL,20,Fheld on Sunday.
